{"title":"Play list Generator in Python","date":"2020-07-03T15:05:41.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 3, 2020","L":"07/03/2020","MM-DD":"07-03"},"link":"2020/07/03/Play-list-Generator-in-Python","tags":["Python"],"updated":"2020-07-03T15:23:18.665Z","content":"<p>We know list generator is a powerful tool, here are some tips of it.</p>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"1-To-Generate-a-Series-of-Random-number\">1 To Generate a Series of Random number<a href=\"2020/07/03/Play-list-Generator-in-Python#1-To-Generate-a-Series-of-Random-number\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">lst = [<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"number\">3</span>,<span class=\"number\">4</span>,<span class=\"number\">7</span>,<span class=\"number\">9</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\">res = [random.uniform(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, sum(lst)) <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> i <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> range(<span class=\"number\">5</span>)]</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(res)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#You'll get five random numbers between 0 and 24</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"Methods of Selection from Genetic Algorithm","link":"2020/07/03/Methods-of-Selection-from-Genetic-Algorithm"},"next":{"title":"OpenAI/Gym Learning Notes","link":"2020/07/03/OpenAI-Gym-Learning-Notes"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2020/07/03/Play-list-Generator-in-Python/","toc":[{"title":"1 To Generate a Series of Random number","id":"1-To-Generate-a-Series-of-Random-number","index":"1"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"custom":"禁止转载-非商用-THSWind"}}